00:47:40.679 --> 00:47:42.679
there's still a URL that is assigned

00:47:43.679 --> 00:47:44.679
to each one of your service.

00:47:45.679 --> 00:47:47.679
All you have to do is know that URL

00:47:48.679 --> 00:47:50.679
and if it's like a RESTful API.

00:47:51.679 --> 00:47:52.679
So you would need to know that URL

00:47:52.679 --> 00:47:54.679
and the verb that you would use.

00:47:55.679 --> 00:47:56.679
So a GET request or a PUT request.

00:47:57.679 --> 00:47:59.679
Postman does a pretty fantastic job

00:48:00.679 --> 00:48:03.679
