00:48:46.679 --> 00:48:49.679
How do we implement the microservices

00:48:49.679 --> 00:48:51.679
within our application architecture?

00:48:52.679 --> 00:48:53.679
How does it overlap with our code

00:48:54.679 --> 00:48:55.679
and version control management

00:48:56.679 --> 00:48:58.679
and our continuous integration, continuous deployment?

