of the infrastructure away from our team.

00:52:35.679 --> 00:52:36.679
We didn't need to know.

00:52:37.679 --> 00:52:38.679
We didn't need to set up.

00:52:39.679 --> 00:52:40.679
Load balancing alone

00:52:41.679 --> 00:52:43.679
was a big concern of ours when we started this.

00:52:44.679 --> 00:52:46.679
Because if you're requesting to an API

00:52:47.679 --> 00:52:49.679
and you have other users requesting to that same API,

00:52:50.679 --> 00:52:51.679
you don't want that one.

00:52:52.679 --> 00:52:53.679
