00:52:54.679 --> 00:52:55.679
so you don't want that one thing

00:52:56.679 --> 00:52:57.679
to be blocking the other users.

00:52:58.679 --> 00:52:59.679
RStudio Connect does a fantastic job of this.

00:53:00.679 --> 00:53:01.679
We've scaled it up to 100 concurrent users

00:53:02.679 --> 00:53:03.679
and not run into an issue.

