00:56:07.679 --> 00:56:08.679
If I hover over it,

00:56:09.679 --> 00:56:10.679
there's information here.

00:56:11.679 --> 00:56:12.679
That information is all encapsulated

00:56:13.679 --> 00:56:15.679
